'''氦合氢离子'''，化学式为HeH<sup>+</sup>，是一个带正电的[[离子|离子]]。它首次发现于1925年，通过[[质子|质子]]（或[[氢正离子|氢离子]]）和[[氦|氦]]原子在气相中反应制得。<ref>{{cite journal|author = T. R. Hogness and E. G. Lunn|title = The Ionization of Hydrogen by Electron Impact as Interpreted by Positive Ray Analysis|url = https://archive.org/details/sim_physical-review_1925-07_26_1/page/44|journal = [[Physical_Review|Physical Review]]|year = 1925|volume = 26|pages = 44–55|doi = 10.1103/PhysRev.26.44}}</ref>它是已知最强的[[酸碱质子理论|布朗斯特质子酸]]，[[质子亲和能|质子亲和能]]为177.8 kJ/mol。<ref name="Epa">{{cite journal|doi = 10.1063/1.555719|author = Lias, S. G.; Liebman, J. F.; Levin, R. D.|year = 1984|title = Evaluated Gas Phase Basicities and Proton Affinities of Molecules; Heats of Formation of Protonated Molecules|journal =Journal of Physical and Chemical Reference Data|volume = 13|pages = 695}}</ref>这种离子也被称为'''氦氢分子离子'''。有人认为，这种物质可以存在于自然[[星际物质|星际物质]]中。<ref>{{cite journal|author = J. Fernandez; F. Martin|title = Photoionization of the HeH<sup>+</sup> molecular ion|journal = J. Phys. B: At. Mol. Opt. Phys|year = 2007|volume = 40 |pages = 2471–2480|doi = 10.1088/0953-4075/40/12/020}}</ref>这是最简单的异核离子，可以与同核的[[氢分子离子|氢分子离子]]H<sub>2</sub><sup>+</sup>相比较。与H<sub>2</sub><sup>+</sup>不同的是，它有一个永久的[[键偶极矩|键偶极矩]]，使它更容易表现出[[光谱|光谱]]特征。<ref>{{cite journal|doi = 10.1006/jmsp.1998.7740|title = Experimental Born–Oppenheimer Potential for theX1Σ+Ground State of HeH+: Comparison with theAb InitioPotential|year = 1999|author = Coxon, J|journal = Journal of Molecular Spectroscopy|volume = 193|pages = 306|pmid = 9920707|last2 = Hajigeorgiou|first2 = PG|issue = 2}}</ref>英国《自然》杂志于2019年4月17日发表相关学术成果：人类初次在太空中检测到了氦合氢离子。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Astrophysical detection of the helium hydride ion HeH +|url=https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-019-1090-x|last=Stutzki|first=Jürgen|last2=Risacher|first2=Christophe|date=2019-04|journal=Nature|issue=7752|doi=10.1038/s41586-019-1090-x|volume=568|pages=357–359|language=en|issn=1476-4687|last3=Ricken|first3=Oliver|last4=Klein|first4=Bernd|last5=Karl Jacobs|last6=Graf|first6=Urs U.|last7=Menten|first7=Karl M.|last8=Neufeld|first8=David|last9=Wiesemeyer|first9=Helmut|access-date=2019-04-18|archive-date=2019-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190418133113/https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-019-1090-x|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 性质 ==
HHe<sup>+</sup>不能在[[凝聚相|凝聚相]]中制备，因为这会使它与任何[[阴离子|阴离子]]、分子、原子发生作用。它可以质子化[[氧气|O<sub>2</sub>]]、[[氨|NH<sub>3</sub>]]、[[二氧化硫|SO<sub>2</sub>]]、[[水|H<sub>2</sub>O]]和[[二氧化碳|CO<sub>2</sub>]]，分别形成{{le|质子化的氧气|Dioxidanylium|O<sub>2</sub>H<sup>+</sup>}}、[[铵|{{chem]]、{{chem|HSO|2|+}}、[[水合氢离子|H<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup>]]和 {{chem|HCO|2|+}} 。<ref name=Gran004/> 其它分子，像是[[一氧化氮|一氧化氮]]、[[二氧化氮|二氧化氮]]、[[一氧化二氮|一氧化二氮]]、[[硫化氢|硫化氢]]、[[甲烷|甲烷]]、[[乙炔|乙炔]]、[[乙烯|乙烯]]、[[乙烷|乙烷]]、[[甲醇|甲醇]]和[[乙腈|乙腈]]也会反应，不过会因为产生的能量太高而直接分解。<ref name=Gran004>{{cite journal |last = Grandinetti |first = Felice |title=Helium chemistry: a survey of the role of the ionic species |journal=International Journal of Mass Spectrometry |date=October 2004 |volume=237 |issue=2–3 |pages = 243–267 |doi = 10.1016/j.ijms.2004.07.012 |bibcode = 2004IJMSp.237..243G }}</ref>但是，可以用[[盖斯定律|盖斯定律]]预测它在水溶液中的酸性：
